### What problem does this feature solve?
- Allows to add possible values of prop;
- Will generate a default validation functions;
- Will be parts of component api;
- Can be used for generate component docs



### What does the proposed API look like?
```javascript
export default {
  props: {
    color: {
      type: String,
      // For type String
      possibleValues: ["red", "green", "blue"],
      // Default validator when has possible values
      // Does not require a definition, can be overridden
      validator: (value, possibleValues) => possibleValues.includes(value)
    },
    delay: {
      type: Number,
      // For type Number
      possibleValues: {min: 0, max: 1000},
      // Default validator when has possible values
      // Does not require a definition, can be overridden
      validator: (value, possibleValues) =>
        (possibleValues.min <= value && value <= possibleValues.max)
    }
  }
  //...
}
```

